Regular version of steam using Warframe as an example
Arch Package Version of steam:
steam steam://rungameid/230410

Flatpak Version of Steam:
flatpak run com.valvesoftware.Steam -applaunch 230410


Warframe has the appID of 230410, which you can find in the URL of a game's store page.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/230410/Warframe/
